'''''Tearing Down the Walls''''' is the fourth studio album by the Swedish rock group [[H.E.A.T]] and first album without the guitarist Dave Dalone. Released in 2014 by the record company Gain/Sony Music. The first single off the album is 'A Shot of Redemption', released a month before the album. The second is 'Mannequin Show'.

